    <div class="comment--content">
      <p>holy moly, molly!  homemade crackers with &#8220;secret cheese™&#8221; (patent pending) may bring me dangerously close to a betrothal of my own.  </></>May I suggest a festive side dish featuring jerusalem artichokes (aka sunchokes)?  Simple yet exotic, comfort food meets unsettling union of potato and artichoke.  Plus, you can get them at the PCC in Fremont (by the raddichio).</p>
